welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Cottage Lake, a charming city known for its beautiful lakes and natural scenery. We invite you to explore and experience the beauty and warmth of our community during your stay here. Enjoy your time in Cottage Lake!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport serves both commercial and general aviation flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is primarily used for cargo and private flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport. Users may need to sign in with a valid email address to access the network.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport handles all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Renton Airport caters to private and corporate flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport for free.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport primarily serves Alaska Airlines and its partners.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves international flights and some domestic flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves primarily domestic flights.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves primarily domestic flights.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse D
terminals.description: Concourse D at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves primarily domestic flights.

terminals.name: Concourse N
terminals.description: Concourse N at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
